references: In recommendation systems, it is well-recognized that even increasing AUC by 1‰ to 2‰ is more than enough to bring online profit. As shown in Tab. 1, our model achieves AUC improvements of 1‰ and 9‰ compared to current state-of-the-art methods across all settings with various embedding sizes. In particular, significant AUC lifts of 9‰ and 6‰ are witnessed with an embedding dimension of 16 on Taobao and Tmall datasets, respectively.
